Feature: Addition
    In Order to avoid silly mistakes
    As a math idiot
    I want to be told the sum of two numbers
    
    Scenario: Add two numbers
        Given I have a calculator
        Given I have entered 42 into the calculator
        And I have entered 99 into the calculator
        When I press add
        Then the result should be 141
    
    Scenario: Add a positive to a negative number
        Given I have a calculator
        Given I have entered 42 into the calculator
        And I have entered -99 into the calculator
        When I press add
        Then the result should be -57
    
    Scenario: Lots of numbers
        Given I have a calculator
        When I add numbers
        Then the result should be
        |Op1|Op2|sum |
        |---|---|----|
        |42 |99 |141 |
        |42 |-99|-57 |
        |-42|-99|-141|
    
    Scenario: Lots of numbers with mapping
        Given I have a calculator
        When I add numbers
        Then the result should be
        |Op1|Op2|sum |
        |---|---|----|
        |42 |99 |141 |
        |42 |-99|-57 |
        |-42|-99|-141|
